Promise. all is very efficeint when it comes to save time. lets suppose consider two independent function which will take independent time
to complete the tasks, if we put them inside then block it will work but takes a lot time, to avoid this we use Promise.alll which executed both 
promises in one go thereby saving time.




Callback vs Promises

Callback mainly has two problems, inversion of control(function where we are using callback function is responsible to call the callback function
if it fails, or calls the callback twice we cant do anything). and another is callback hell

whereas promises give assurity by giving two options namely then and catch